<h1 id="toc0"><span>Anomaly Classification System (ACS) Guide</span></h1>
<hr />
<div class="step_container">
<h1 id="toc1"><span>What is ACS?</span></h1>
<blockquote>
<p>ACS is a new classification system that adds further depth to the already existing Object Class system. <strong>It is not intended to replace the current Object Class system. It is only meant to enhance it.</strong></p>
</blockquote>
