<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-4"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-4')">4</a>. <a href="https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/vlam">Dutch for Flame</a>, generally a candle flame.</div>
